autiful","count":1},{"word":"keep","count":1},{"word":"going","count":1},{"word":"credits","count":1},{"word":"year","count":1},{"word":"danger","count":1},{"word":"amazing","count":1},{"word":"startorch","count":1},{"word":"academy","count":1},{"word":"sharing","count":1},{"word":"into","count":1},{"word":"unknown","count":1},{"word":"student","count":1},{"word":"wait","count":1},{"word":"start","count":1},{"word":"new","count":1},{"word":"chapter","count":1},{"word":"life","count":1},{"word":"missing","count":1},{"word":"today","count":1},{"word":"wish","count":1},{"word":"family","count":1},{"word":"crowd","count":1},{"word":"hear","count":1},{"word":"male","count":1},{"word":"female","count":1},{"word":"happy","count":1},{"word":"everything","count":1},{"word":"hoped","count":1},{"word":"worry","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Haha! Your thesis or your delicious stew, either works! I'm not picky!","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":114000031},{"text":"As for the Void Storm… I'll try all your ideas. The problem is, we don't understand the Void Storm deeply enough.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":114000031},{"text":"Especially in the depths with high Voidmatter concentration… No probe survives the journey, so research is stuck. I can't shake the feeling that...","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":114000031},{"text":"Nah-uh, they love playing with me! Why else would they crawl over and play before running away?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":114000031},{"text":"And my lessons—ahem, {PlayerName}, you promised me another level of Split Stars! No take-backs!","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":114000031},{"text":"But... I want to learn how you folded that thing first. Can you show me? Pretty please?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":114000031},{"text":"Yeah! Mine always nose-dives right away, but yours flew so far! How?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":114000031},{"text":"...Oh, okay. You promise?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":114000031},{"text":"—May we one day walk among the stars, to touch with our own hands a universe so cold, so real, and so breathtakingly beautiful.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"That's all from me. If I keep going, my credits this year might be in danger!","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"It's an amazing feeling to be here at Startorch Academy, and to know I'll be sharing this journey into the great unknown with all of you. As a student, I can't wait to start this new chapter of my life.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"There's just one thing missing today... I wish my family could be here in the crowd to hear this.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"So, to {Male=him;Female=her}, I want to say: I'm doing great. And I'm happy. Everything is just as you hoped it would be. So please, don't worry about me.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001}]}